{"tid":2284522,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府：「香港制造」制裁影響有限 聯匯制度運作良好","createTime":"2020-11-13T10:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T11:06:45.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e6997cb8915de60a33caa6635727f902d0a6b68","tid":2284522,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"歐錫熊：本港經濟已見底 美國單方面制裁影響有限<br />\n<br />\n政府經濟顧問歐錫熊認為，從數字上看，第2季經濟已經見底，而內地經濟有望延續增長，或會有利本港出口，但要關注外圍疫情仍可能影響環球貿易往來。<br />\n<br />\n歐錫熊強調，美國單方面對港制裁，帶來的影響有限，特別是對貿易的影響輕微，但整體投資信心仍要視乎環球經濟前景，相信在新型肺炎疫苗廣泛應用之前，經濟仍然充滿陰霾。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，目前本港聯匯制度運作十分良好，在過去數月亦有明顯資金由海外流入香港，反映市場對聯匯制度有很強信心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559905-20201113.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559905-20201113.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIiwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=3b0428d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559905-20201113.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=49610a01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559905-20201113.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"dc501a01963f78855292f1938aeb8b41d8712396","tid":2284522,"uid":64337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"咁仲唔派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252ddae273b631e5652bcf9bb04ea1daab460d67","tid":2284522,"uid":80610,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T10:58:36.000Z","msg":"侵侵：有方向了，就依兩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2afcc0033bc73dca02ee1f36e3af0a34822c2c6","tid":2284522,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:03:21.000Z","msg":"等拜登上台就冇事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=